                                                                                                                           6                                                                                      Business Briefs
                              
	 New Delhi, Feb. 24: The Essar group is selling its telecom tower business  Essar Telecom Infrastructure  to American Tower in an all-cash deal. The deal values Essar Telecom Infrastructure at an enterprise value of around Rs 2,000 crore.                             
	 Mumbai, Feb. 24: Promoters of Bajaj Auto today sold over 10 lakh shares to another promoter entity  Bajaj Holdings amp; Investment  in an open market deal valued at around Rs 180.45 crore.
                                                                                                                          
